    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is a total stunner! This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and it drives like a dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, so there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. You really have to see it in person to believe how perfect it is! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a look!",
      "price": 43900.0,
