      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, boasting individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the critical VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural integrity. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The suspension maintains factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers. With zero paint imperfections and a cockpit free of bolster wear, this specimen is a concours-ready benchmark for the chassis.",
